# Campfire Overhaul - Project Rules for AI Agents

## CRITICAL: Read Before Any Implementation

This mod's core philosophy is **IMMERSIVE WORLD INTERACTION**, not crafting-table convenience.

## ‚õî NEVER DO

1. **NEVER add crafting table recipes** for:
   - Unlit Campfire
   - Firewood (item or block)
   - Any future campfire-related components
   
2. **NEVER create shortcuts** that bypass the physical building process

3. **NEVER replace** the vanilla campfire - we enhance its CREATION, not its behavior

## ‚úÖ ALWAYS DO

1. **Use world-placed block interactions** (right-click mechanics)
2. **Follow the progression**: Chop ‚Üí Stack ‚Üí Fuel ‚Üí Light
3. **Use vanilla textures** where possible
4. **Keep mechanics intuitive** - discoverable through experimentation

## The Campfire Building Flow (CANONICAL)

```
[Stump] ‚Üê ONLY crafting table recipe allowed (3 logs)
    ‚Üì
[Log on Stump] ‚Üí Right-click ‚Üí [4x Firewood items]
    ‚Üì
[Place Firewood] ‚Üí Stack to 4 ‚Üí [Firewood Stack block]
    ‚Üì
[Add ANY fuel] ‚Üí [Unlit Campfire block]
    ‚Üì
[Flint & Steel] ‚Üí [Vanilla Campfire] üî•
```

## Quick Reference

| Component | How to Obtain |
|-----------|---------------|
| Stump | Craft: 3 logs in row |
| Firewood | Chop log on stump |
| Firewood Stack | Place & stack firewood |
| Unlit Campfire | Add fuel to 4-stack |
| Lit Campfire | Flint & Steel on unlit |

## Before Implementing Any Feature

Ask yourself:
1. Does this require a crafting table? ‚Üí **Probably wrong approach**
2. Can this be a world interaction? ‚Üí **Do this instead**
3. Does it fit "realistic campfire building"? ‚Üí **If no, reconsider**

